---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = "Digitful - Real Growth";
const pageDescription = "Digitful delivers real growth with innovative digital strategies.";
const pageCanonical = "https://digitful.ca/";
---
<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} canonicalUrl={pageCanonical}>
    <main>
<section class="hero py-6 d-flex align-items-center min-vh-75">
          <div class="container text-center">
            <h1 class="fs-1 fw-bold mb-3">Pure Marketing, Real Growth</h1>
            <h2 id="typewriter" class="fs-5 fs-4 mb-4">You've tried the Hacks. Guesswork ends here.</h2>
            <a href="#services" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 py-2">See What's Possible</a>
          </div>
        </section>
        
<section class="about-us py-6 bg-dark bg-gradient">
          <div class="container text-center">
            <div class="row align-items-center gy-5 gx-md-5">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h2 class="mb-4">About Us</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-3">We're not another agency selling you tactics. We're marketers who understand business.</p>
                <p class="mb-3">Our approach is simple: we focus on what actually moves the needle for your business, not vanity metrics.</p>
                <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-outline-light mt-3">Learn More</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
<section id="services" class="services py-6">
          <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Our Services</h2>
            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-4 g-4">
              <div class="col">
<a href="/social-media/" class="card h-100 text-decoration-none text-white border-secondary rounded-lg shadow-sm hover-shadow-lg">
                  <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up fs-1 mb-3 text-info"></i>
                    <h3 class="card-title h5 mb-2">Social Media</h3>
                    <p class="card-text mb-0">Stop posting. Start building.</p>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col">
<a href="/seo/" class="card h-100 text-decoration-none text-white border-secondary rounded-lg shadow-sm hover-shadow-lg">
                  <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <i class="bi bi-search fs-1 mb-3 text-success"></i>
                    <h3 class="card-title h5 mb-2">SEO</h3>
                    <p class="card-text mb-0">Traffic's not your problem. Relevance is.</p>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col">
<a href="/paid-ads/" class="card h-100 text-decoration-none text-white border-secondary rounded-lg shadow-sm hover-shadow-lg">
                  <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <i class="bi bi-badge-ad fs-1 mb-3 text-warning"></i>
                    <h3 class="card-title h5 mb-2">Paid Ads</h3>
                    <p class="card-text mb-0">Reach real buyers, not scroll zombies.</p>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col">
<a href="/automation/" class="card h-100 text-decoration-none text-white border-secondary rounded-lg shadow-sm hover-shadow-lg">
                  <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <i class="bi bi-gear fs-1 mb-3 text-danger"></i>
                    <h3 class="card-title h5 mb-2">Process Automation</h3>
                    <p class="card-text mb-0">Stop doing. Start automating.</p>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
<section class="cta py-6 bg-primary">
          <div class="container text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4">Ready to grow your business?</h2>
<p class="fs-5 mb-4">Let's talk about your goals and how we can help you achieve them.</p>
            <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-light btn-lg px-4">Get Started</a>
          </div>
        </section>
        
<section class="testimonials py-6">
          <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5">What Our Clients Say</h2>
<div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4">
              <div class="col-md-4">
<div class="card h-100 border-secondary rounded-lg shadow-sm hover-shadow-lg">
                  <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-text mb-3">"Digitful transformed our approach to digital marketing. Their focus on real results instead of vanity metrics made all the difference."</p>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-3">
                      <img src="/testimonial-1.jpg" alt="Client" class="rounded-circle me-3" width="50" height="50">
                      <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0 h6">Sarah Johnson</h5>
                        <small class="text-muted">CEO, TechStart</small>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
<div class="card h-100 border-secondary rounded-lg shadow-sm hover-shadow-lg">
                  <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-text mb-3">"We've worked with several agencies before, but Digitful's strategic approach and focus on ROI has been refreshing and effective."</p>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-3">
                      <img src="/testimonial-2.jpg" alt="Client" class="rounded-circle me-3" width="50" height="50">
                      <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0 h6">Michael Chen</h5>
                        <small class="text-muted">Marketing Director, GrowthCo</small>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
<div class="card h-100 border-secondary rounded-lg shadow-sm hover-shadow-lg">
                  <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i>
                      <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-text mb-3">"The automation solutions Digitful implemented saved us countless hours and helped us scale our marketing efforts efficiently."</p>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-3">
                      <img src="/testimonial-3.jpg" alt="Client" class="rounded-circle me-3" width="50" height="50">
                      <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0 h6">Jessica Williams</h5>
                        <small class="text-muted">Founder, EcoStyle</small>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
